import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"reduced"}}>{`re:duced`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`A typesafe functional toolbelt for Redux`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
